{"type": "article", "id": 50842, "title": "同样生活在大城市，你和别人的差距怎么这么大？", "description": "", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 269276, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "<p><style> @font-face{ font-family:\"Times New Roman\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"宋体\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"Calibri\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"微软雅黑\"; }  p.MsoNormal{ mso-style-name:正文; mso-style-parent:\"\"; margin:0pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; mso-pagination:none; text-align:justify; text-justify:inter-ideograph; font-family:Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; }  span.msoIns{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:underline; text-underline:single; color:blue; }  span.msoDel{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:line-through; color:red; } @page{mso-page-border-surround-header:no; \tmso-page-border-surround-footer:no;}@page Section0{ } div.Section0{page:Section0;}</style></p><p><font face=\"微软雅黑\">现在的都市生活现状，</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">人们每天在城市里穿梭</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">，急促的步伐踏上拥挤的地铁是为了赶上打卡</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">签到与无休无止的</font>concall。无限的繁忙让人还没来得及享受刚取得的小成就，就又前赴后继扑向下一个项目。埋头于琐碎的邮件和未读消息，更使人摆脱不了日复一日的焦虑感和层峦堆叠的过劳肥。年初你兴致冲冲地写下今年的wish list<font face=\"微软雅黑\">，</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">年末在角落发现那张纸时才惊觉一年到头</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">什么都没完成。</font></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306180308Og9WT5AV4fFznRBw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.416667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">但反观周围，身边总有些人的生活无比多彩，充实又精致。夏天感受巴黎埃菲尔铁塔脚下的优雅，冬天享受着狮城夜里的宁静。朋友圈的状态不是旅行在路上，就是在新开幕的艺术展览上和大师作品合照，就算是空中飞人常常出差，也秉承play hard work hard信念，保持自己最好状态。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803061127111DoEPXT6HV3NUB0s.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p><style> @font-face{ font-family:\"Times New Roman\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"宋体\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"Calibri\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"微软雅黑\"; }  p.MsoNormal{ mso-style-name:正文; mso-style-parent:\"\"; margin:0pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; mso-pagination:none; text-align:justify; text-justify:inter-ideograph; font-family:Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; }  span.msoIns{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:underline; text-underline:single; color:blue; }  span.msoDel{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:line-through; color:red; } @page{mso-page-border-surround-header:no; \tmso-page-border-surround-footer:no;}@page Section0{ } div.Section0{page:Section0;}</style></p><p>而你一有空就窝在家里自诩为“佛系女孩”，抱着手机可以从早到晚葛优躺，离不开快递和外卖。这一切不禁让你反思起来： 我真的生活在便利丰富的大城市吗？没错，你究竟错过哪些让你成为精致女孩的重要时刻，我们有了以下的发现和建议。<br></p>"}